%% Diagram: SSR/RSC hydration timeline and where mismatches happen
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Srv as Server (RSC + SSR)
    participant Net as Network
    participant Br as Browser
    participant JS as Client JS bundle
    participant LS as localStorage / cookies

    Srv->>Net: HTML + RSC payload + dehydrated cache
    Net->>Br: First byte (TTFB)
    Br->>Br: Paint static HTML
    Net->>JS: Hydration bundle arrives
    JS->>Br: hydrateRoot(...)
    Note over JS,Br: React renders client tree and<br/>compares to server HTML
    alt Tree matches
        JS->>Br: Attach event handlers (interactive)
    else Mismatch (theme, locale, time, persisted store)
        JS-->>Br: Console warning + client re-render
        Note over JS,LS: Triggered by reading window.localStorage,<br/>Date.now(), navigator.language, etc.<br/>during render
    end
    Br->>LS: Read persisted UI state (post-hydration)
    Br->>JS: TanStack Query: useSuspenseQuery reads warm cache
